{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/10755", "repo": "rails", "body": "Most people who start a basic single instance mongrel, especially for the first time, *will* see the message, in my opinion. More advanced configurations such as running in the background may hide the message, but it's the basic users who would benefit most from the warning. \r\n\r\nIf you do switch to binding by default, there has to be a switch like `--no-binding` (or should it be `--global-binding` or `--bind-all`?) to turn if off for those who for whatever reason need the current behaviour. And a startup message should then explain it, probably.", "_id": {"$oid": "5237dbf2bd3543c151008926"}, "issue_id": 10755, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/18480745", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/10755#issuecomment-18480745", "updated_at": "2013-05-27T03:10:19Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg", "login": "egilburg", "gravatar_id": "cc4f5494a8dcaaf577e678cb3901dab6", "html_url": "https://github.com/egilburg", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/cc4f5494a8dcaaf577e678cb3901dab6?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F552d65b6e9616642fd0217dc7f8361bd.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 242532, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2013-05-27T03:07:23Z", "id": 18480745, "owner": "rails"}
